Here is Step-by-step Process of Applications--
--------------------------------------------------------------

1) Setup email details in .env
2) Migrate the db
3) Laravel package to automatically create register/login pages and some authentication controllers for us.
          a) composer require laravel/ui
          b) php artisan ui vue --auth
          c) npm install && npm run dev

4) Implements MustVerifyEmail in User Model.
5) Configure the route
6) add 'verified' middleware in HomeController.